_sText:
You have lost your color... Get it back!
========================================
**Short and quite simple bhop map with some kz mixed in.**

Original map was created by Yeckoh for our Zombie Master 1 bunnyhop server back in 2012. The intention was to create a really simple map that even new bhoppers could beat. We then decided to port it to CSS (along with some others maybe :>). We improved on it a little and then forgot about it for a while... Here it is!

I am releasing it on behalf of Yeckoh.
--------------------------------------

Legit/400vel possible.
